0.007   2017-09-20 (PERLANCAR)

	- Second attempt of fixing escaping on Win32, thanks to Vadim Repin
	  [RT#123031] ref: http://perlmonks.org/?node_id=1199727.


0.006   2017-09-19 (PERLANCAR)

        - [Bugfix] Fix escaping for Win32, only backslash that is followed by
          another backslash or is the last backslash shall be escaped
          [RT#123031].

        - Allow overriding OS with $OS package variable.


0.005   2017-08-16 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Specify minimum version of Exporter 5.57 (allows use without
	  inheriting) [CT].


0.004   2017-01-04 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Avoid use of 'warnings' to reduce startup overhead.


0.003   2016-12-27 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Fix failing test, avoid use of 5.10-ism (defined-or) [CT].


0.002   2016-12-26 (PERLANCAR)

	- Fix failing tests on Unix [CT].


0.001   2016-12-25 (PERLANCAR)

        - First release.
